 Stokes suffered a bruised thigh on the second play of the season-opening 
victory against Tennessee, and though he said he would play against Southern 
Methodist on Saturday, was unable to do so.Without the biggest of their 
big-play men, the Bruins staggered to a 17-10 victory. 
</P>
