cornerback after Greenwood suffered a broken right ankle Saturday. . . . Chad 
Overhauser, a redshirt freshman, stepped in for Paul Kennedy when he suffered a 
knee injury. Kennedy, a senior, is sidelined for the season, leaving the Bruins 
shallow on the offensive line. JIM HODGES 
