<TEXT>
<P>
 Prep Extra: Beginning today, the Times Orange County launches a special 
supplement devoted to high school sports.On Tuesdays, Prep Extra will appear as 
a separate section, behind Sports, that includes features, statistics, athletes 
of the week, notes and a column by staff writer Chris Foster; today's section 
focuses on this year's seniors to watch, leading off with Newport Harbor 
volleyball star Misty May. During the fall, Saturday Sports will contain a Prep 
Extra pullout devoted to football. 
</P>
<P>
 Daily Coverage: The Times will continue to publish comprehensive team scores 
and individual highlights on daily events in Sports. 
</P>
