TITANS' COLBERT RULED INELIGIBLE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Shefonda Colbert, a two-year starter at forward for the Cal State Fullerton 
women's basketball team, has been ruled academically ineligible and was not 
readmitted to the university for fall classes. 
</P>
<P>
 Colbert, a former Lynwood High star, averaged 10.6 points as a freshman and 
9.3 last season as a sophomore. She led the team in rebounding last season with 
an 8.8 average. 
</P>
<P>
 She started all 27 games for a team that was 5-22 last season. 
