<DOCNO> LA091394-0164 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 078716 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
September 13, 1994, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
