<TEXT>
<P>
 Medical Properties Inc., an Encino real estate investment trust, said last 
week its secured lender, Foothill Capital Corp., would complete foreclosure 
proceedings against all of Medical Properties' remaining assets within the 
week.The company said it will then cease business operations. Its board of 
directors will also soon resign. 
</P>
