<HEADLINE>
<P>
VENTURA COUNTY REVIEW / JACK SEARLES: MERGER NOT EXPECTED TO AFFECT TRAVEL 
OFFICES; BRIEFLY: 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Jack Searles 
