<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A German tourist aboard a sightseeing boat circling Manhattan was hit in the 
back Monday by a bullet apparently fired from the shore. Rolf Bolowski, 31, of 
Hamburg was hospitalized in stable condition. It was unclear if he was the 
intended target. 
</P>
