</P>
<P>
 What is the best city or community in Orange County for unmarried people like 
yourself to live? Newport Beach: 15% Huntington Beach: 12% Irvine: 7% Anaheim: 
5% Laguna Beach: 4% Costa Mesa: 4% Fullerton: 3% Orange: 2% Mission Viejo: 2% 
