<P>
 Train service -- A story Saturday on Amtrak service in Camarillo may have been 
unclear. Amtrak service will begin Oct. 30, without station improvements that 
Amtrak had requested from the city. The improvements have been made 
unnecessary, due to changes in scheduling for Metrolink trains, which use the 
same station, according to a Ventura County Transportation Commission 
spokesman. 
</P>
